{{Top|leg}}
'''Rendeel Industries''', located on [[Rendili/Legends|Rendili]], was a large [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]]-manufacturing corporation. In addition to conventional plants, they also built facilities both in space and underwater, in order to process a variety of foods such as [[Quekka fish]]. These underwater processing plants were composed of several modules, engineered to withstand deep ocean pressures. Rendeel also was a large provider of [[Starship/Legends|starship]] consumables.

